Title: Relates to high deductible health plans and health savings accounts; relates to the effectiveness of a chapter of the laws of 2025
Summary: Relates to cost sharing requirements for high deductible health plans and health savings accounts; relates to the effectiveness of a chapter of the laws of 2025.
LawCode: Amd §§3216, 3221 & 4303, Ins L; amd §4, Chap of 2025 (as proposed in S.6895-A & A.5367-A)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, in relation to high deductible health plans and health savings accounts; and to amend a chapter of the laws of 2025 amending the insurance law relating to high deductible health plans and health savings accounts, as proposed in legislative bills numbers S. 6895-A and A. 5367-A, in relation to the effectiveness thereof
